  "name": "Week 8.2 - Over Under's 4x 4min",
  "note": "This ride is what we refer to as \"Over Under's\". Over Under is when you go above FTP (100%) to below FTP (<100%). During this ride you will perform 4 sets of 30 seconds over your threshold at 105% of your FTP followed by 30 seconds under your threshold at 85% of your FTP for 4-minutes. Imagine going back and forth from Vo2 to Sweet Spot. Between each set you will have 2 minutes of recovery. (by Kristin Armstrong)",
